## Installation

### pip (for Claude Desktop/Code)

```bash
pip install mcp-{name}
```

### From source

```bash
git clone https://github.com/verygoodplugins/mcp-{name}
cd mcp-{name}
pip install -e .
```

### Claude Desktop Configuration

Add to your Claude Desktop config (`~/Library/Application Support/Claude/claude_desktop_config.json`):

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "mcp-{name}": {
      "command": "python",
      "args": ["-m", "mcp_{name_underscore}.server"],
      "env": {
        "API_KEY": "your_api_key"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

